Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.48,wood,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&H616161&\bord0\b1\fn@楷体\frz271.7\pos(643.95,182)}以下训练生任命为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.48,wood,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&H616161&\bord0\b1\frz270\fn@楷体\pos(530.663,208)}正规卫人驾驶员 \N
