Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:45.38,wood,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&HF9FF73&\bord0.2\3c&HFFF68B&\b1\pos(72.875,45.333)}Heigus诱导\N海中浮游槽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,十分好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我做给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,认证 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,之后的搭乘手续我来办理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,即将开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 怎么回事啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想两个人乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,即将关门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谷风 快把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,即将开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,两名乘客 确认搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,即将关门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.38,Default top,,0,0,0,,欢迎乘坐Heigus诱导海中浮游槽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.84,Default top,,0,0,0,,即将突入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为了您的安全请握紧扶手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是完整路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是两周
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总之到最近的出口下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,又被关起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.00,wood,,0,0,0,,{\c&H737373&\bord0\b1\fn@楷体\pos(657.388,239.333)\frz268.6}希德尼亚新报\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.00,wood,,0,0,0,,{\c&H737373&\bord0\b1\fn@楷体\pos(597.575,203.333)\frz267.9}岐神家第八代当家 长男诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.11,wood,,0,0,0,,{\c&H737373&\bord0\b1\frz0\fn楷体\pos(549.875,148.667)}出生之时就拥有一切的贵公子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.11,wood,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&H737373&\bord0\b1\fn@楷体\frz268.2\pos(759.888,400.667)}岐神财阀公子哥 \N才色兼备的接班人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的全部都是靠自己的力量得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 最棒的武具和名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你从我面前把这两样夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,前进方向 偏32度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,纵向-13度发现巨大物体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,距离5万千单位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,疑似复数的本体结合巨大的胞衣而形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,连结型奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,连结型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么一直都没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,胞衣呈透过状态潜伏着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可视化的家伙发现我们后采取的行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快编成讨伐队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人选就交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,生命是从海中诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至少地球是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谷风来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人飘荡在宇宙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在海中一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样能不能回到海中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,星白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,东第二出击口 西第四出击口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,卫人发射口 准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶员请迅速搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,接近中的连结型奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,突破第三警戒线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要磨磨蹭蹭的了 弦打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谷风 因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信 能走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,回病房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,仄她们 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎那 奇居子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是怎么到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 脸色不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再…再睡会比较好 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
